{
  "text": "A provisional forest cover map was established based on a reconnaissance survey. Land at an elevation of 1000 m to 1700 m a.s.l. was selected for the study, as forest occurred in all three conservation zones within this range. The study area consisted of 73 ha in the core zone, 115 ha in the buffer zone and 22 ha in the restoration zone. A grid system with 1400 cells was created and overlaid on the study area to randomly place the sample plots. Forty plots of 20 m \u00d7 20 m were established in each conservation zone, with the center of each plot located in the center of a selected cell [CITATION_1] .",
